                    "value": "<p>The slithering rift makes a single pseudopod Strike against each target within range it hasn’t already @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Grabbed]{Grabbed}.</p>\n<p>These attacks count toward the slithering rift’s multiple attack penalty, but this penalty doesn’t increase until after all of these attacks.</p>"
